>gawia</i> ‘territory’, <i>walah</i> ‘stranger’, or <i>gisil</i> ‘pledge’. Medieval forms can be found to support all these theories, and it is possible that several names have fallen together, or that the name was subjected to reanalysis by folk etymology at an early date."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Geoffrey De Eydon was born in 1180, in Northamptonshire, England. He had at least 1 daughter with Mrs. De Hyden. He died in 1209, in Forest of Dean, Gloucestershire, England, at the age of 29."},"et":{"1180–1209":"1180–1209","1187–Female":"1187–Surnud","1200–1294":"1200–1294","1200":"1200","1187":"1187","1294":"1294","1209":"1209","1180":"1180","Forest of Dean, Gloucestershire, England":"Forest of Dean, Gloucestershire, England","Northamptonshire, England":"Northamptonshire, England","Scotland":"Scotland"},"fi":{"1180–1209":"1180–1209","1187–Female":"1187–Kuollut","1200–1294":"1200–1294","1200":"1200","1187":"1187","1294":"1294","1209":"1209","1180":"1180","Forest of Dean, Gloucestershire, England":"Forest of Dean, Gloucestershire, England","Northamptonshire, England":"Northamptonshire, England","Scotland":"Scotland"},"fr":{"1180–1209":"1180–1209","1187–Female":"1187–Décédée","1200–1294":"1200–1294","1200":"1200","1187":"1187","1294":"1294","1209":"1209","1180":"1180","Forest of Dean, Gloucestershire, England":"Forest of Dean, Gloucestershire, Angleterre","Northamptonshire, England":"Northamptonshire, Angleterre","Scotland":"Écosse","lifeSummary":"Geoffrey De Eydon est né en 1180, à Northamptonshire, Angleterre. Il a eu au moins 1 fille avec Mrs. De Hyden. Il est décédé en 1209, à Forest of Dean, Gloucestershire, Angleterre, à l’âge de 29 ans."},"de":{"1180–1209":"1180–1209","1187–Female":"1187–Verstorben","1200–1294":"1200–1294","1200":"1200","1187":"1187","1294":"1294","1209":"1209","1180":"1180","Forest of Dean, Gloucestershire, England":"Forest of Dean, Gloucestershire, England","Northamptonshire, England":"Northamptonshire, England","Scotland":"Scotland","lif